rkshires when we were kids. Little Yorkshire terriers, and then when that - was put to sleep, my father bought - }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4594632\charrsid14287120 P}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3367996\charrsid14287120 
ekinese. He bought a pet }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4594632\charrsid14287120 P}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3367996\charrsid14287120 
