\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3765441 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3367996\charrsid14287120 No, I don't remember when we were children but I remember - wh
ile we were courting and that and after we were married we all - always had the - Daily Express. Mm.
