\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3765441 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3367996\charrsid14287120 The bo}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4594632\charrsid14287120 d}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3367996\charrsid14287120 
y, yes. Yes. Yes.
