k from Luton to Harpenden, which was five miles, and back - when we were kids. Yes. And we lived a mile from the town up, so that made it six miles, each way.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1580481 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3367996\charrsid14287120 You'd go for tea or something would you?
