Oh yes. Oh yes, right until she died, she was eighty-six when she died and - they had her up in Luton to live for the last year or so because she wasn't very well but she wasn't happy. She'd always lived at Harpenden. Alw
ays had a nice garden and - you know, plenty of everything going on around her. Plenty of friends, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1580481 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3367996\charrsid14287120 Would you go visiting neighbours with mother?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3765441 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3367996\charrsid14287120 Well our neighbours, we were all - very friendly you know. I used to do for one of the neighbou
rs, take the kids out, wash up for her, clean all her cutlery. Clean all her corners out and - do - all sorts of things.
