\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1580481 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3367996\charrsid14287120 What about going out shopping?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3765441 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3367996\charrsid14287120 Yes, I used to do all the shopping. I used to do all the shopping for the neighbour one side, and my mother. I got everyt
hing - from the groceries on Friday dinner time I used to have a golden sovereign to go with - for the groceries, and it used to come to about nineteen and something ha'penny you know, always got enough, I could always treat meself to a little bar of choc
olate, for fetching it you know, you could get a bar of chocolate then for about three}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4594632\charrsid14287120  }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3367996\charrsid14287120 
ha'pence. Always used to fetch the meat. The joint and the meat. And everything, I always did the shopping.
