he garden. He used to take us to the garden, and - when he went shooting. Sometimes he'd take a couple of us. And - we used to go picking flowers you know and - probably - take - a can or a flask, well - I don't think there were flasks when we were tiny, 
they was mostly cans. Everything used to be in cans with little lids you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1580481 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3367996\charrsid14287120 Like the enamel ones?
