\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1580481 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3367996\charrsid14287120 But this one you were talking about was covered?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3765441 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3367996\charrsid14287120 This was a - it was actually - a business - a business like - where there would be a motor van
 take things now on the road, this was like what they called a carrier. Couple of horses and a covered wagon type of things, and if we were lucky and we could get - on the wagon, you know, we all used to get to Harpenden on the wagon. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1580481 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3367996\charrsid14287120 Did you do anything special for Bank Holidays do you remember?
