\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1580481 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3367996\charrsid14287120 Did you ever go away for a holiday to stay away?
