 love that. And then I fancied I'd like to be a dancer you know. But of course I was too big, my mother used to say, you're too big for a dancer. You've got to be tiny. But my sister that was tiny never wanted to dance. But I did. And I used to dance - I 
used to - dance on me toes, and nobody'd stop me dancing. But when I got older I went off of it, I never wanted to dance when I got older, I never bothered. Mm.
