\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3765441 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3367996\charrsid14287120 Well my mother was very shy. Even at the d
og shows, when we used to show dogs, she loved her dogs, she did everything for them, brushed them, used to disinfect them, shampoo them, they were }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12656273\charrsid14287120 \endash }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid3367996\charrsid14287120  her}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12656273\charrsid14287120  }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3367996\charrsid14287120 
idol after we grew up, but when it comes to the show she'd die at the thoughts of taking it round the 
ring, I had to do that. And she couldn't sort of - talk to the people and discuss things with them. I think she was so busy bringing a family up, four under ten years, that - she made that her whole life. And then it made her rather shy.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1580481 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3367996\charrsid14287120 You said that she had a thing about children that were scruffy and lousy and didn't want you to mix with them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3765441 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3367996\charrsid14287120 Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1580481 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3367996\charrsid14287120 Did father feel the same way about it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3765441 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3367996\charrsid14287120 Yes, I think - I think he did, though - he wouldn't have said so much, my mother was the ruling hand. With us children, yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1580481 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3367996\charrsid14287120 Do you think that your mother saw herself as belonging to the same social class as your father?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3765441 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3367996\charrsid14287120 Oh yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1580481 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3367996\charrsid14287120 Do you think it was possible at that time to move from class to another?
\par 
