\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3765441 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3367996\charrsid14287120 I used to like her. Yes. She was a good}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12656273\charrsid14287120  }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid3367996\charrsid14287120 hearted woman, she used to make us die of laughing, I could always see the funny sid
e of it. And of course I didn't really understand what this - prostitution was I mean - I didn't even know I don't think at that time that you had to have a man before you could have a baby and that sort of thing. Not until I was ever so old. No. Because 
I
 always remember there was a girl we worked with, she was getting fat and they kept saying she was going to have a baby, and - I thought it was 'cos she ate Quaker Oats, I said she eats a lot of Quaker Oats, they're ever so fattening. And I didn't know un
til she had this baby and they said it must be a soldier you know. I was quite old, seventeen then. Yes. - Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1580481 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3367996\charrsid14287120 Were you ever given lessons by your parents or privately?
